WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:01.893
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.893 --> 00:00:02.891
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.891 --> 00:00:04.880
Thank you for joining me again today.

00:00:04.880 --> 00:00:10.311
Yesterday's video, I felt like we made some good ground in the spirit when we prayed.

00:00:10.311 --> 00:00:11.840
I felt it all day long.

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:16.727
We had pushed a major boulder out of the way, and we have much more work to do.

00:00:18.342 --> 00:00:29.120
When the Lord was talking to me about the visions and the things that he is showing me—the critics thinking that it's familiar spirits—I told you we're here to give all the glory to God.

00:00:29.120 --> 00:00:32.800
Everything we do in word and in deed, we give all to the glory of God.

00:00:34.239 --> 00:00:40.719
The Lord was saying, 'People try to compare you to a psychic, son, and I don't want them putting you in that box.

00:00:40.719 --> 00:00:48.080
You walk in a prophetic mantle, and what I've called you to do is to be a watchman and tell my people what's coming.

00:00:48.080 --> 00:00:54.400
' But right now, the focus is too much on you, and I want them to focus more on prayer.

00:00:54.400 --> 00:01:03.889
We must put our attention on Jesus for what's coming, and we must pray for the days ahead because the days are evil.

00:01:03.889 --> 00:01:10.429
We see great things happening already in the news and the media concerning major weather events.

00:01:11.420 --> 00:01:22.240
If we go back to what the Lord showed us on November 11th, I saw a major ice storm coming to America that would be genetically modified.

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:26.240
It's like weather warfare, weather manipulation.

00:01:26.530 --> 00:01:33.360
I saw an ice storm coming from the Oklahoma area all across America that would be over a stretch of a thousand miles.

00:01:33.760 --> 00:01:46.479
If anybody remembers that, I saw deep purple in this, and the Lord said those are ice percentages—how much ice this place will get.

00:01:47.866 --> 00:01:56.000
It was a crippling ice storm, so much so that it shut power out for some cities for up to three weeks or a month.

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:57.173
It was bad.

00:01:57.173 --> 00:02:03.474
And the Lord said to me, 'Brandon, I have given you power and authority on this earth.

00:02:03.474 --> 00:02:15.229
If you take authority with your prayer group and pray, you will be just like me speaking to the storm at the Sea of Galilee and telling it to be still.

00:02:15.229 --> 00:02:17.600
' Peace came over the storm.

00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:25.486
You have the same ability; as he is, so are we in this world, to pray over your area.

00:02:25.851 --> 00:02:39.840
If you are a believing believer, I'm telling you, it's time to rise up and use your God-given authority over the weather—praying over the storms, praying over this ice storm, and praying over your power.

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:43.120
It's not meant for us to go without power for that long.

00:02:43.120 --> 00:02:49.980
It's not meant for us to have crippling weather that messes up our trees and our roofs.

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:53.584
I believe we can pray over this and shift it.

00:02:55.760 --> 00:03:00.000
I believe that we can do a lot of things through the power of the name of Jesus.

00:03:00.352 --> 00:03:01.232
This is one of them.

00:03:01.232 --> 00:03:08.960
I want you to see this clip real quick of what the Lord showed us concerning the ice storm on November 11th.

00:03:10.811 --> 00:03:16.039
Braden, correct me if I'm wrong, but I want you to listen to it and I'll be right back with you.

00:03:16.039 --> 00:03:23.783
The Lord told us, 'You're about to see weather manipulation, weaponized weather more than what you've ever seen before.

00:03:23.783 --> 00:03:37.519
' He said that even last night with ice storms, winter cyclones with heavy snowfall, blizzard conditions in Buffalo, and lake-effect snow that will be the largest we've ever seen.

00:03:38.696 --> 00:03:42.840
I saw major weather events in the days ahead.

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:45.620
Well, you say, 'Well, Brandon, we have weather events all the time.

00:03:45.620 --> 00:03:47.897
' Yes, but this is going to be different.

00:03:47.897 --> 00:03:49.726
I saw major winds and straight-line winds.

00:03:49.726 --> 00:03:58.080
I saw power outages that would go for a thousand miles—just crippling ice storms.

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:04.708
And the Lord said, 'You have to pray over the weather.

00:04:04.708 --> 00:04:20.604
' That's when the Lord showed me there'll be snowstorms in the days ahead where there'll be so much snow in an area people will have to dig themselves out of their houses because there's so much snow that falls in such a short amount of time.

00:04:20.604 --> 00:04:24.080
It will look like something biblical.

00:04:24.526 --> 00:04:32.080
Snowstorms as tall as their houses, and people were digging themselves out, buried in snow in certain cities.

00:04:32.080 --> 00:04:33.1000
It's never happened before.

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:42.343
I don't know what the average house height is, maybe 8 feet of snow if you're digging yourself out of your house.

00:04:44.200 --> 00:04:45.856
That's a lot of snow.

00:04:45.856 --> 00:04:56.224
Meteorologists have described it as the heaviest snowfall in 146 years, with some areas receiving over three months' worth of snow in just a few days.

00:04:56.224 --> 00:05:10.080
I saw ice storms that went from Oklahoma all the way up—crippling ice storms—and lost power for a long time because the purple was so deep.

00:05:10.920 --> 00:05:18.000
It was a terrible ice storm that went clear through Arkansas, Tennessee, and Kentucky.

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:27.600
It was different shades of pink, purple, and black.

00:05:28.384 --> 00:05:31.520
I thought that was interesting.

00:05:31.520 --> 00:05:35.119
Major ice storms over a thousand miles long.

00:05:37.840 --> 00:05:42.617
You might say, 'Well, Brandon, you said a thousand-mile-long time.

00:05:42.617 --> 00:05:45.715
' Okay, so that's what the Lord warned us, and here we are.

00:05:46.053 --> 00:05:54.168
We are right at that point in time this weekend for a major ice storm that the Lord warned us was coming.

00:05:54.168 --> 00:05:56.373
So, what are we going to do about it?

00:05:57.867 --> 00:05:58.526
We're going to pray.

00:05:59.568 --> 00:06:08.462
The other part is I have a great caution concerning our president and him being over in Switzerland right now for the safety of his life.

00:06:08.462 --> 00:06:21.559
As I was praying over him talking in his speech, saying, 'Hey, it's been 365 days; it's been a year since we were inaugurated and in office, and look at all that we've done.

00:06:21.559 --> 00:06:27.950
We've busted all these people,' and he mentioned ICE and the success of his presidency over one year.

00:06:31.940 --> 00:06:49.919
I had such a caution about all that's about to take place, and the Lord said, 'I told you over the next two weeks to pray over the valley of decision all the way up until the 26th, going into the 3rd of February.

00:06:49.919 --> 00:07:12.000
' Remember, this is a time frame for black swan events for the Olympics on February 6th, praying over our nation concerning the Super Bowl, praying over major events concerning the United States of America.

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:16.112
We made it through the college championship; nothing happened.

00:07:16.112 --> 00:07:17.733
All glory to God.

00:07:17.733 --> 00:07:23.386
I believe it was a high time that they could have done something, but they didn't.

00:07:23.386 --> 00:07:27.039
So, we're praying over our churches.

00:07:27.039 --> 00:07:33.092
The Lord keeps bringing up churches, so we'll pray over them tonight.

00:07:33.092 --> 00:07:35.559
We're going to pray over the water.

00:07:35.559 --> 00:07:41.863
Last night, I was praying over the deep and the water.

00:07:41.863 --> 00:07:57.680
I saw deep trenches and volcanic eruptions about ready to go off and major catastrophic events about to take place with tsunami waves, volcanic eruptions, and earthquakes.

00:07:58.537 --> 00:08:04.169
They're talking about all these auroras, solar flares, and the sun.

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:15.200
There'll be major activity in your sun, and this is a sign of the end times.

00:08:16.640 --> 00:08:23.736
I get real with you: I get excited about all this stuff because I'm looking up because I know my redemption draws nigh.

00:08:25.719 --> 00:08:34.413
If you don't know Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior, it's time for you to come to the saving knowledge of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:08:34.826 --> 00:08:36.479
It's a heart thing.

00:08:36.479 --> 00:08:40.799
I want you to know that Jesus Christ loves you and has a plan for your life.

00:08:40.799 --> 00:08:45.440
As you're watching this video today, it's not by accident.

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:58.213
We're praying for you, for the lost, for people to get born again, and for the baptism of the Holy Ghost, that people would find a deeper, intimate relationship with the Father.

00:09:02.859 --> 00:09:04.560
To those that knock on the door, he's there and ready to open it.

00:09:04.560 --> 00:09:07.500
That those who are seeking him will find him.

00:09:07.500 --> 00:09:14.160
I believe in 2026 it'll be a year for your intimate relationship with the Father.

00:09:14.500 --> 00:09:24.720
What was dry in your life all through the past will be a time of a great river of growth and like a tree planted by the water.

00:09:24.720 --> 00:09:38.720
You're going to be drinking from that Holy Ghost water as you come to this channel on a day-to-day basis, praying with me that your intimacy with the Father will go deeper and you'll have more than a saving knowledge of the Lord Jesus.

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:45.856
You'll have an intimate knowledge of the Lord Jesus—that he loves you and that he has a plan for your life.

00:09:46.168 --> 00:09:49.200
I'm not here to scare you; I'm here to prepare you.

00:09:49.200 --> 00:09:58.446
I believe that God has put me in this position to come on here and warn the people of that which is to come.

00:09:58.446 --> 00:10:04.427
Signs follow them that believe, and I believe we're just walking in the Great Commission.

00:10:04.427 --> 00:10:09.040
We're going to go into all the world, laying hands on the sick and they'll recover, casting out devils.

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:12.354
We will lay hands on the blinded eyes and they'll open.

00:10:12.354 --> 00:10:13.360
We'll raise the dead.

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:17.359
We'll do all the things that the Lord Jesus Christ commissioned us all to do.

00:10:17.359 --> 00:10:24.880
It shouldn't be shock and awe when we see it happen, but I thought it was interesting.

00:10:26.399 --> 00:10:41.985
My wife did a college paper when she was in college; it was on church growth and planting, and she did this church growth and planting class at ORU in 2013.

00:10:42.713 --> 00:10:49.004
It was the statistics of how long a church makes it and all the things that happen with a major church.

00:10:49.004 --> 00:10:59.669
So I put that in the community thread on our channel to show the statistics about how many churches do not lead people to Jesus.

00:10:59.669 --> 00:11:07.260
It was the statistics on how many people are witnessing and their salvation being taught and people going out evangelizing.

00:11:07.260 --> 00:11:11.330
The numbers were staggering of how bad it really was.

00:11:11.680 --> 00:11:23.699
Regardless of how many people say, 'Hey, Brandon, the only reason you get a lot of people saved on this channel is because you scare them to Jesus,' I say, 'No, I'm trying to warn you.

00:11:23.699 --> 00:11:27.320
' Because I warn you of what's coming is not to scare you.

00:11:27.320 --> 00:11:34.079
I'm not trying to scare you to Jesus; I'm trying to tell you the truth, and it's not sugarcoated.

00:11:34.079 --> 00:11:38.436
If you don't accept Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior, you're going to hell.

00:11:38.773 --> 00:11:41.410
People go, 'How can you say that?

00:11:41.410 --> 00:11:45.680
' I didn't have to; the Bible did.

00:11:45.680 --> 00:11:49.340
I'm not trying to tell you anything that the Bible hasn't already warned you about.

00:11:49.640 --> 00:11:53.470
A preacher may try to tell you that you can't tell people they're going to hell.

00:11:53.470 --> 00:12:00.720
I don't have to tell you you're going to hell; the Bible tells you you're going to hell if you don't accept Jesus Christ.

00:12:00.720 --> 00:12:03.760
There is no other way to the Father unless it's through him.

00:12:03.760 --> 00:12:10.720
If you don't confess Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior, ladies and gentlemen, you're going to spend eternity in hell.

00:12:10.720 --> 00:12:11.080
Why?

00:12:11.080 --> 00:12:13.600
Because the Bible told us we would.

00:12:13.600 --> 00:12:18.200
So there's no fear in that; that's just truth.

00:12:18.200 --> 00:12:23.965
And sometimes truth will scare the poo out of you because you're living in sin.

00:12:23.965 --> 00:12:31.520
And if you're living in sin and you're not serving the Lord Jesus Christ, the Bible says you're going to hell.

00:12:31.840 --> 00:12:35.760
That's just the blatant truth.

00:12:35.760 --> 00:12:40.928
If you're living in a bad homosexual relationship, you're going to hell.

00:12:40.928 --> 00:12:43.360
That's just the truth.

00:12:43.360 --> 00:12:47.519
People don't want to hear it, but I'm here to tell you the truth.

00:12:47.933 --> 00:12:52.640
I have pastors say, 'Hey, you know, brother, you can't scare people to Jesus.

00:12:52.640 --> 00:13:00.365
' I'm not scaring them to Jesus; I'm trying to tell them the truth of what God's Word said.

00:13:00.365 --> 00:13:05.839
And in doing so, they're being convicted and running to Jesus.

00:13:05.839 --> 00:13:07.920
All glory to God, ladies and gentlemen.

00:13:07.920 --> 00:13:09.849
It isn't Brandon Biggs doing any of this.

00:13:11.170 --> 00:13:14.519
I'm telling you, I'm just an average guy that was a janitor for 15 years.

00:13:14.519 --> 00:13:17.710
And the Lord said, 'Go on YouTube and tell them I'm coming, son.

00:13:17.710 --> 00:13:25.839
I'm going to show you things and I'm going to do things in your ministry that have never been done before.

00:13:25.839 --> 00:13:33.710
' I think the body of Christ a lot of times rejects things that are new because they're used to the old.

00:13:33.710 --> 00:13:38.742
But he said, 'Behold, I'm going to do something new in these last days, and I'll do it through you, Brandon.

00:13:38.742 --> 00:13:41.060
' I said, 'Well, what is that?

00:13:41.060 --> 00:13:45.980
' 'I'm going to show you things, and I want you to tell them what's coming, so they can pray over it.

00:13:45.980 --> 00:13:54.411
' So, in shocking the elders, a lot of times they get freaked out over stuff and they go, 'You know, that looks like it's an occultic thing, brother.

00:13:54.411 --> 00:13:59.600
' But all I'm doing is telling you that Jesus is coming.

00:13:59.600 --> 00:14:04.320
He said, 'I'm bringing out new mantles and new giftings that the world has never seen before.

00:14:04.320 --> 00:14:07.680
Will you be a part of it?

00:14:07.680 --> 00:14:16.263
' And I saw chariots of fire in heaven with packages of mantles and giftings for end times that the world has never seen before.

00:14:16.469 --> 00:14:22.079
He said, 'Behold, I'm going to do something new that I've never done on this earth before.

00:14:22.079 --> 00:14:29.227
' But the elders, a lot of times because they hadn't seen it before, automatically label it witchcraft or darkness.

00:14:29.227 --> 00:14:29.653
'Ooh, that's darkness.

00:14:30.507 --> 00:14:32.110
I don't know about that.

00:14:32.110 --> 00:14:33.110
We better check it.

00:14:33.110 --> 00:14:34.747
We better test the spirits.

00:14:34.747 --> 00:14:35.440
' That's true.

00:14:35.440 --> 00:14:36.220
You should.

00:14:36.220 --> 00:14:37.780
Thank God you do.

00:14:37.780 --> 00:14:46.399
But so much in testing it, you reject everything that God's trying to do—something new in somebody's life—and you say, 'Hey, we've got to hold that at bay.

00:14:46.399 --> 00:14:48.560
We can't have that in our church.

00:14:48.560 --> 00:14:49.931
' That's kind of weird.

00:14:52.996 --> 00:14:53.253
I don't know.

00:15:04.095 --> 00:15:04.911
He sees it all the time.

00:15:09.680 --> 00:15:12.830
And the Lord said, 'Brandon, I want you to package it a little differently.

00:15:17.270 --> 00:15:20.480
And how you see, I show you stuff, but even how you do it, I want you to be careful on it.

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:23.480
I want you to do it this way.

00:15:23.480 --> 00:15:31.165
' He's instructed me for the elders, and I do it all for him because he wants them to pray.

00:15:31.165 --> 00:15:33.413
They know how to pray.

00:15:33.413 --> 00:15:35.960
He wants them to come along.

00:15:50.826 --> 00:15:57.040
And I learned this: you just got to keep pushing on regardless of the elders, regardless of the young people.

00:15:57.989 --> 00:16:01.955
I'm just here to tell you Jesus loves you.

00:16:05.787 --> 00:16:09.800
And I'm so thankful that you would take your time every single day out of your busy schedule.

00:16:09.800 --> 00:16:12.479
So much in America is busy, busy, busy.

00:16:12.479 --> 00:16:16.560
So I'm going to try to keep it under an hour.

00:16:16.560 --> 00:16:18.436
Here we are, probably at 15 minutes.

00:16:34.159 --> 00:16:34.559
I've said plenty now.

00:16:34.559 --> 00:16:36.400
All glory to Jesus.

00:16:36.400 --> 00:16:37.360
Here we go.

00:16:37.360 --> 00:16:38.320
Ready to pray?

00:16:45.570 --> 00:16:50.079
You all forget that whenever I'm in the Spirit, I can go out and I hear conversations, and I'm only saying things that I've heard in the Spirit—people talking.

00:16:51.668 --> 00:16:59.360
And so I'm allowed to say certain things, but the Lord said, 'Be very cautious in how you walk on this.

00:16:59.360 --> 00:17:05.839
' I hear people talking, big ministers, and the Lord will allow me to hear what they're saying about me.

00:17:11.920 --> 00:17:12.160
And he said, 'I'll let you hear this, but I want you to correct this and keep marching on.

00:17:12.160 --> 00:17:14.680
' It challenges them to grow.

00:17:14.680 --> 00:17:19.1000
He goes, 'A lot of the time it has nothing to do with you, Brandon.

00:17:19.1000 --> 00:17:24.400
It's challenging them in their old stinking way of thinking.

00:17:35.946 --> 00:17:36.292
I'm trying to pull them out of their ditch by using somebody new like you who is polishing.

00:17:36.292 --> 00:17:38.159
' Do you understand?

00:17:38.159 --> 00:17:44.160
I'm rough like sandpaper, and I rub people wrong, I've learned.

00:17:47.039 --> 00:17:52.720
They try to be nice to your face, but they aren't, and I love them anyway.

00:17:54.799 --> 00:17:56.799
Because I realize that people are just people.

00:17:56.799 --> 00:17:58.280
Does that make sense?

00:17:58.280 --> 00:18:06.391
You've got to love people regardless of whether they talk trash about you.

00:18:11.747 --> 00:18:14.720
And that's people that you've been thinking of as friends, and you go, 'Well, that's all right.

00:18:14.720 --> 00:18:15.920
Just keep walking on.

00:18:15.920 --> 00:18:16.708
Keep marching.

00:18:26.630 --> 00:18:26.820
I don't answer to you.

00:18:28.914 --> 00:18:29.200
I answer to Jesus.

00:18:29.200 --> 00:18:30.800
' Do you understand?

00:18:36.444 --> 00:18:36.676
And that's what a lot of you will have to do in the days ahead.

00:18:36.676 --> 00:18:43.280
Because a lot of the elders, a lot of old people, they'll try to hold you back.

00:18:43.280 --> 00:18:50.144
They'll try to say, 'Hey, this is the way we've done it.

00:18:50.144 --> 00:19:08.559
' And the Lord said, 'I'm going to have to remove them because they're being a hindrance to the flow of what I'm trying to do, and they're about to go home early, and I'll raise up Davids and elders that will not be a bump in the road, causing me to say, 'Well, this is how we've always done it.

00:19:18.040 --> 00:19:21.707
This is the way we always will do it.

00:19:21.707 --> 00:19:24.000
'' No, no, no.

00:19:24.000 --> 00:19:28.526
"Behold, I do a new thing," He said.

00:19:32.860 --> 00:19:35.080
"And I'm going to do new things in the next generation in this timeframe because what you did is over.

00:19:35.600 --> 00:19:39.879
And they can't use old bait to get the new fish.

00:19:39.879 --> 00:19:50.190
They're going to have to use something new because the world is not the same world as it was in the fifties, the sixties, and the forties.

00:19:50.190 --> 00:19:53.584
We're in a new generation, folks.

00:20:02.090 --> 00:20:02.340
" And He said, "We've got to attract them in somehow.

00:20:02.340 --> 00:20:07.040
" But it's always to attract, to deflect, and bring them to Jesus.

00:20:19.880 --> 00:20:20.250
You've got to have new bait in this generation, and the old way of thinking has to change.

00:20:20.250 --> 00:20:22.170
That's what the Lord was showing me about that.

00:20:22.170 --> 00:20:30.240
So I'm not here to embarrass anybody or call their name out whose conversations I heard; the Lord allowed me to.

00:20:34.382 --> 00:20:36.879
I wish I could because they need to be corrected, but the Lord said, "It's not your place.

00:20:36.879 --> 00:20:43.679
I'm doing it and I'm using you to do it, and they don't even realize it.

00:20:43.679 --> 00:20:47.439
" So I say, "Okay, Lord, I humble myself and keep going.

00:20:47.439 --> 00:20:50.229
Remember the janitor; remember the janitor, son.

00:20:50.229 --> 00:20:52.729
" All right, let's take communion together.

00:20:52.729 --> 00:20:55.689
Who wants to take communion?

00:20:59.748 --> 00:21:06.976
I know I went a little longer, but I just wanted, for the people who need to hear it, it's time to come up higher.

00:21:06.976 --> 00:21:16.080
So here we go with our body with the Lord for what He did for us.

00:21:16.080 --> 00:21:21.119
Father, I thank You, Lord, that You died for us.

00:21:22.519 --> 00:21:27.004
I thank You, Lord, that You rose again on the third day.

00:21:27.004 --> 00:21:32.477
I thank You, Lord, that we're healed and whole and well by Your stripes.

00:21:33.195 --> 00:21:42.320
And Father, we take this body in Jesus' name and we lift it up before You.

00:21:42.320 --> 00:21:50.080
We sit at Your feet boldly because, Jesus, You paved the way.

00:21:50.080 --> 00:21:52.620
Thank You, Father, for the body.

00:21:52.620 --> 00:22:00.840
Thank You, Lord, for all that You've done for us, and thank You, Lord, that You healed us by Your stripes.

00:22:14.207 --> 00:22:14.495
We take this in the name of Jesus.

00:22:14.495 --> 00:22:17.039
Lord, we thank You for the blood.

00:22:17.039 --> 00:22:21.120
We make much of the blood; the blood makes much of us.

00:22:21.120 --> 00:22:30.150
We apply the blood of Jesus over us, and we apply the blood of Jesus over our sin.

